S44M_G3A_U01_RUNTIME_ROUTE_QAFIX_STATUS

sourceId = g3a_u01_3a01
status = WAITING_FOR_LOCAL_TEST

root_cause:
- S44L promoted new G3A-U01 KPs into the selector.
- Their PatternSpec IDs were not yet registered in the browser PatternDefinition layer.
- The worksheet generator route did not yet dispatch G3A-U01 number-structure PatternSpecs to the S44I-S44K generator.
- Browser UI therefore failed with batch_a_pattern_not_available.

fixed:
- added G3A-U01 number-structure PatternDefinitions
- added G3A-U01 number-structure worksheet route
- added validator delegation for G3A-U01 number-structure text questions
- added worksheet runtime regression tests for each new KP and mixed new-KP worksheet

local_check:
- git pull public main
- npm test
- git status

next = S44M_G3A_U01_MixedWorksheetQA after local tests pass
